You guys dont like getting hit right? Well when a Sorcerer is in your group let him mez the additional mobs(put them to sleep). Once they are asleep you can assist the main tank in killing each one individually. When you cast an area effect spell and break the mez that the sorcerer cast, expect to get yer ass chewed(and deservedly so)because you very likely caused the death of the whole group. This happend 4 times before we booted that wizard out of our group.
