Yes Malle I did about 4 times. People are afraid to say "I dont understand". I usually give the Mez explaination and what NOT to do when I get into a group. I ask people to send me tells if they dont know what /assist or AoE means. Recently a very good Cleric that has a wonderfull way of explaining things has helped alot. He says "be sure you understand because i wont heal mez breakers." After that is said I get tells asking what /assist is and other Mez related questions. It is tough love but works great. No one has died because of breaking Mez since in our groups.
